        %p Our first program offering will be targeted toward rising executives. Our goal is to provide a broad and relevant curriculum for talented employees managing others for the first time, those whose management responsibilities have expanded, and those who have been identified as high-performing individuals with the potential to be future leaders. Typically, these will be employees who are 4 to 10 years into their careers. The McKinsey Management Program will include eight courses that will be completed over 9 to 12 months. Each course will require 2 to 3 hours of work per week over 6 weeks. The first cohort of students will begin the McKinsey Management Program in Summer 2014.
